0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"如果純粹係想剿起小小&amp;細盒<br />\nthen?"},{"pid":"4ccffab31e8f3becfaf3ed54f111ead668a07244","tid":457280,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33c93150d463d66992affd07922c19ad71608994","tid":457280,"uid":135811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>紅 ice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好耐冇聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣覺得隻蜜瓜味好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n擠出嚟己經濕濕地，勁易搓均<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲可以輕鬆摔到髮尖同髮根都有泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要唔笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8daf35c32c0d02aa1daa07f1190df43b68b8b5cf","tid":457280,"uid":52617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T15:43:57.000Z","msg":"Architex 07 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f542751a525786c6395eb77d13a5947e5ef779","tid":457280,"uid":36817,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:20:28.000Z","msg":"新手可以試下紅ice<br />\n聽講幾年前好興 越出越差之後就少左人用<br />\n但係就平 屈臣氏都應該有<br />\n唔推薦 Faddy Gatsby <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中階價位既有<br />\nHans De Fuko - Quicksand <br />\nMorris Motley - Styling Balm <br />\n<br />\nQuicksand 係乾身泥黎<br />\n頭髮睇落會無咁油 幾日無洗頭都唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMorris Motley 價錢貴其他牌子成倍<br />\n但盒泥個容量就多人成倍<br />\n之前高登好多人吹奉用Morris Motley <br />\n夠力hold"},{"pid":"9996f0c4e63015ea77516cde7908f1ea57e42194","tid":457280,"uid":35325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T20:18:22.000Z","msg":"Morris Motley 市面上綜合黎講最好嘅選擇 基本上咩髮型都用得"},{"pid":"e50c654e6f8c40de7fc2833c7e82993ccca07b26","tid":457280,"uid":152773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T03:19:18.000Z","msg":"強烈推薦！solid rock! 乾爽 容易handle, 我都係天生曲髮，呢一隻可以做到layer 感 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/111804_079606e88dead33f18701278f39b980a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F111804_079606e88dead33f18701278f39b980a.jpg&h=78f8734f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23df03ba69536ebdf30b3ae7f32691e1153d650a","tid":457280,"uid":148679,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"巴打如果睇你要求<br />\nHans De Fuko - Quicksand就岩你啦<br />\n佢正價出面做緊大約150<br />\n我有盒用左幾次嘅姐<br />\n有時講邊個產品適合你唔夠<br />\n始終系要自己真系上左頭先知岩唔岩自己<br />\n因為每個人都唔同髮質<br />\n你有興趣嘅話留tg <br />\n平d比你又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於你樓下個d gas b faddy就唔好買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個d產品十年前都唔會用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb5053f8dfffeb8f1dfc76c8f3c2a79bac38f9d","tid":457280,"uid":78379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:14:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/161253_5d0e94b3f775374486181b3cc56a7ee8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F161253_5d0e94b3f775374486181b3cc56a7ee8.jpg&h=0b42c77a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本果隻MARO 好好用，可以gel 到成廚師帽咁高."},{"pid":"285d4d0012f578adc0e72f82fff0a8a3d75a3269","tid":457280,"uid":60065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.price.com.hk/product.php?p=270214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fproduct.php%3Fp%3